            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is almost cooked, stir the <strong>squash purée</strong> and <strong>soft cheese </strong>through the risotto</p><p>Add the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until the cheese has melted and the rice is cooked – this is your<strong> butternut squash risotto</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
