            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>butternut squash risotto </strong>topped with the <strong>cheese shavings</strong>, <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>roasted butternut squash</strong>, <strong>crispy sage leaves </strong>and <strong>toasted pecans</strong></p><p>Season with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
